%80%EC%A7%80%EA%B3%A0-%EC%9E%88%EB%8B%A4"><span class="toc-number">1.6.</span> <span class="toc-text">NFT아트와 피지컬아트는 다른 문법을 가지고 있다</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%EC%BA%94%EB%B2%84%EC%8A%A4%EC%97%90-%EA%B7%B8%EB%A6%B0-%EA%B7%B8%EB%A6%BC-%EC%82%AC%EC%A7%84-%EC%B0%8D%EC%96%B4-NFT%EB%A1%9C-%EC%98%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%A9%B4-%EB%90%A0%EA%B9%8C"><span class="toc-number">2.</span> <span class="toc-text">캔버스에 그린 그림, 사진 찍어 NFT로 올리면 될까?</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%EA%B7%B8%EB%A0%87%EB%8B%A4%EB%A9%B4-%EA%B8%B0%EC%A1%B4%EC%97%90-%ED%94%BC%EC%A7%80%EC%BB%AC%EC%95%84%ED%8A%B8-%EC%98%81%EC%97%AD%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%ED%99%9C%EB%8F%99%ED%95%98%EB%8D%98-%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%8C%EB%93%A4%EC%9D%80-%EC%96%B4%EB%96%BB%EA%B2%8C-%EC%A7%84%EC%9E%85%ED%95%B4%EC%95%BC%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%EA%B0%80"><span class="toc-number">2.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">그렇다면 기존에 피지컬아트 영역에서 활동하던 사람들은 어떻게 진입해야하는가</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#NFT-%EC%95%84%ED%8A%B8%EB%A5%BC-%EC%B2%98%EC%9D%8C-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4%EB%A9%B4"><span class="toc-number">2.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">NFT 아트를 처음 시작한다면</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%EB%AC%B4%EC%97%87%EC%9D%B4-NFT%EA%B0%80-%EB%90%A0-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EB%8A%94%EA%B0%80"><span class="toc-number">2.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">무엇이 NFT가 될 수 있는가</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%ED%95%B5%EC%8B%AC%EC%9D%80-%E2%80%98%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98-%EA%B2%83%E2%80%99%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%9E%91%ED%92%88%EC%9D%84-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%9C%EB%8A%94-%EA%B2%83"><span class="toc-number">2.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">핵심은 ‘나의 것’으로 작품을 만드는 것</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%EC%96%B4%EB%96%A4-NFT%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%B4%EA%B9%8C"><span class="toc-number">2.5.</span> <span class="toc-text">어떤 NFT를 살까</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%ED%95%9C%EC%A4%84%ED%8F%89"><span class="toc-number">3.</span> <span class="toc-text">한줄평</span></a></li></ol>
